l University (KazNU), Kazakhstan\" tabindex=\"-1\" >\n\t\t\tRead More \u00bb\t\t</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</article>\n\t\t\t\t<article class=\"elementor-post elementor-grid-item post-1771 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-kazakhstan\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__card\">\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-post__thumbnail__link\" href=\"/north-kazakhstan-state-university\" tabindex=\"-1\" ><div class=\"elementor-post__thumbnail\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1080\" height=\"740\" src=\"../../wp-content/uploads/2025/02/North-Kazakhstan-State-University.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1774\" alt=\"North Kazakhstan State University\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"../../wp-content/uploads/2025/02/North-Kazakhstan-State-University.jpg 1080w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2025/02/North-Kazakhstan-State-University-300x206.jpg 300w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2025/02/North-Kazakhstan-State-University-1024x702.jpg 1024w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2025/02/North-Kazakhstan-State-University-768x526.jpg 768w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2025/02/North-Kazakhstan-State-University-24x16.jpg 24w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2025/02/North-Kazakhstan-State-University-36x25.jpg 36w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2025/02/North-Kazakhstan-State-University-48x33.jpg 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" /></div></a>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__badge\">Kazakhstan</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__avatar\">\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\" src=\"../../wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Atlas-Mentor-Circle-White-New-150x150.png\" class=\"avatar avatar-128 photo\" alt=\"atlasmentor\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"../../wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Atlas-Mentor-Circle-White-New-150x150.png 150w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Atlas-Mentor-Circle-White-New-300x300.png 300w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Atlas-Mentor-Circle-White-New-768x768.png 768w, ../../wp-con